      "message": "Patch Set 5: Looks good to me, approved\n\n(1 inline comment)\n\nThis is probably a good patch for b2_1/b2_2, since it is minimally intrusive and has bee tested already.\n\nOn master, however, it conflicts directly with the SMP ptlrpc thread rework recently landed in http://review.whamcloud.com/2878 and also being done in http://review.whamcloud.com/2879.\n\nThe remaining part that addresses the HP reconnect should be rebased after that patch lands (or it could be rebased on top of that change before it lands and added as a dependent patch).",
